query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `notification_preferences` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `globalMute` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `muteTradeExecuted` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `muteTradeError` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `mutePositionOpened` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `mutePositionClosed` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `muteWebhookFailed` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `muteDailyDigest` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `emailEnabled` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  `emailAddress` varchar(320),
  `inAppEnabled` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  `soundEnabled` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `notification_preferences_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
)
